</dt><dd><div style="">SW Naito Pkwy and Salmon St <a href="http://trimet.org/go/cgi-bin/plantrip.cgi?to=SW+Naito+Pkwy+and+Salmon+St&amp;by=5:30+p.m.&amp;on=06/22/11" target="_BLANK" title="TriMet trip planner"><img alt="Take Trimet" src="images/trimetrose.gif" border="0"></a></div>
