<br>if you have them. &nbsp;We'll have some extra. &nbsp;Meet on the 
lawn north side of the Salmon Street Fountain. &nbsp;Then we'll ride 
across the Hawthorne Bridge and out the Springwater Corridor Trail with a
 stop at Sellwood Park for some juggling practice, a quick dip in the 
Willamette, and finish at Reed College where we will join the Portland 
Jugglers at their weekly gathering for a juggle-off.</em>
