<dt style=""><a name="22-2282" style="">COMMUNITY GARDEN TOUR</a>
<a href="#22-2282"><img src="images/chain.gif" alt="Link" title="Link to this event" border="0"></a>
</dt><dd><div style="">Alberta Coop Grocery, parking lot, NE 15th Ave and Alberta St <a href="http://trimet.org/go/cgi-bin/plantrip.cgi?to=NE+15th+Ave+and+Alberta+St&amp;by=6:15+p.m.&amp;on=06/22/11" target="_BLANK" title="TriMet trip planner"><img alt="Take Trimet" src="images/trimetrose.gif" border="0"></a></div>
6:15pm - 8:45pm<div style="">
<em>The Alberta Coop &amp; OSALT invite you to a tour of four very 
different gardens in inner NE Portland. In a fairly short-distance ride,
